convert 
------------------------------------------------------------

Simple PDB file conversion tool. Takes as input a file called 

pdb.map 

in the current directory 

pdb.map contains a map from the current format to the desired format 

Example: 

This changes the residue names 
RMAP   rG  G
RMAP   rU  U
RMAP   rC  C
RMAP   rA  A


This changes the atom names
//Backbone 
AMAP   P   P  
AMAP   O1P OP1
AMAP   O2P OP2
AMAP   O5* O5'
AMAP   C5* C5'
AMAP   C4* C4'
AMAP   O4* O4'
AMAP   C3* C3'
AMAP   O3* O3'
AMAP   C2* C2'
AMAP   O2* O2'
AMAP   C1* C1'

//Guanine Specific
AMAP  1H2  H21
AMAP  2H2  H22

//Cytosine Specific
AMAP  2H4  H42
AMAP  1H4  H41

//Adenosine Specific
AMAP  2H6  H62
AMAP  1H6  H61
